{"id": 1932, "genre": 1001, "title": "你最烦哪种办公室失礼行为？", "description": "不一定是有意为之，但还是妨害到了别人（特别是在上班已经足够令人暴躁的情况下）。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 6187, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170928140621DF1B8IieaH0VNkWG.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-28T06:28:39Z", "options": [{"id": 238848, "content": "一些令人不愉快的外号", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650623}, {"id": 238849, "content": "见过一两次就开始问个人隐私，很多人的饭桌上问女生年龄", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830923}, {"id": 238850, "content": "偷看别人聊天，关注别人隐私，说过的话总是不承认，不干活还接私活，影响别人的，不遵守规章制度的，开会要等半天的各种。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143616}, {"id": 238851, "content": "大声卡痰并且吐在废纸篓里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007248}, {"id": 240899, "content": "不说一声过来抽我纸巾用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079810}, {"id": 238852, "content": "领导布置工作思路混乱，多问几句还给脸色", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 381208}, {"id": 238855, "content": "动别人东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918502}, {"id": 238856, "content": "滔滔不绝但说不到重点，善意提醒话题转而争论是否说到了重点这种无意义的对话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904076}, {"id": 239881, "content": "安排任务时问题一堆，要提交了死活联系不上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040580}, {"id": 240393, "content": "被上司教训了回来就走办公室大声咒骂上司。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148391}, {"id": 238859, "content": "不告而取", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715331}, {"id": 238860, "content": "上班时间外放听音乐?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143677}, {"id": 238861, "content": "和家里人吵架后把情绪带到公司来，发泄给同事下属", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1123962}, {"id": 251917, "content": "各种牢骚   对我的设计稿有意见时 会用尖尖的指甲戳我屏幕吱吱响", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199177}, {"id": 238862, "content": "做微商的同事给我推销我根本不需要的东西......", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111636}, {"id": 238863, "content": "每天跟你讲自己的家长里短（尴尬而不失礼貌的微笑）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515073}, {"id": 239634, "content": "和销售没法沟通，聊着聊着就是洗脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007515}, {"id": 240916, "content": "共用垃圾桶中吐痰", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115078}, {"id": 238875, "content": "讲话时突然凑过来看你手机/电脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753653}, {"id": 243235, "content": "上司一个劲儿的要求你，自己确做不到。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1134375}, {"id": 238887, "content": "在网吧打游戏的时候对面的人脱了鞋，而且脚很丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137809}, {"id": 238892, "content": "人身攻击，还当开玩笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098150}, {"id": 238895, "content": "传播谣言", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143783}, {"id": 239151, "content": "不喜欢负能量的人逼逼叨叨，把她家七大姑子八大姨的破事儿，絮叨个没完，不论你和谁聊天，她总能插上嘴，恨不得把嘴给她钉起来！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093814}, {"id": 238903, "content": "休息的时候大声说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391490}, {"id": 245307, "content": "在办公室唱歌 在办公室吹口哨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212460}, {"id": 238909, "content": "大声笑 又笑得恶心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142809}, {"id": 241472, "content": "办公桌连在一起 而对面的 就像抽筋一样 天天抖腿 走路脚不离地 拖来拖去\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980888}, {"id": 238917, "content": "自己在做事，讨厌有人在旁边指指点点……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143858}, {"id": 239942, "content": "说话根本跟不上节奏，而且还有很多听不懂的问题，还有很多完不成的事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160770}, {"id": 246343, "content": "公众大声粗言秽语", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174851}, {"id": 238922, "content": "首先是看别人的电脑！其次是我作为领导，你是下属，你总打断我讲话！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 238923, "content": "每次讨论和吵架一样，互怼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086979}, {"id": 240459, "content": "上司大声叫我名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 975573}, {"id": 238926, "content": "看你能力不错 帮我做这个报告吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137519}, {"id": 239438, "content": "“你怎么不说话 我看看你平常都干啥”然后就把脸凑近我的电脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 344666}, {"id": 238927, "content": "经过偷瞄 偷瞄不走。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141431}, {"id": 240207, "content": "妨碍别人思考工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096193}, {"id": 241487, "content": "不冲厕所?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152929}, {"id": 240465, "content": " 大声讲话，公众场合抽烟，还有放歌跟大声", "image": "img/option/option/20171007131523789S3bBfFTUcGqWw", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148901}, {"id": 239190, "content": "拉是非", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548420}, {"id": 239707, "content": "你急他不急，耽误事还怪你", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211089}, {"id": 238684, "content": "每次开会的时候都姗姗来迟，害全部人等着", "image": null, "praise_count": 133, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 241244, "content": "在办公场所/时间，做私人护理的琐事比如剪指甲化妆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152716}, {"id": 238685, "content": "在别人努力工作的时候高谈阔论", "image": null, "praise_count": 389, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 238686, "content": "不及时回邮件、或生硬地只回一个词", "image": null, "praise_count": 167, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 238942, "content": "老板总是突然跟我说有工作要做", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104019}, {"id": 238943, "content": "带着孩子来公司，不止一次，孩子还喜欢吵", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143946}, {"id": 238945, "content": "在办公室宣泄消极情绪，大发脾气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022231}, {"id": 238690, "content": "deadline前一秒钟才把做的东西上交，而且问题很多", "image": null, "praise_count": 344, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}]}